            <lg xml:id="TK851">
<l>ikaleṉpa vellā vuyirkkum pakaleṉṉum</l>
<l>paṇpiṉmai pārikku nōy</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The disease which fosters the evil of disunion among all creatures is termed hatred by the wise.</l>
